      | QUARKUS_INFINISPAN_CLIENT_USE_AUTH        | true              |
      | QUARKUS_INFINISPAN_CLIENT_USERNAME   | IamNotExist       |
      | QUARKUS_INFINISPAN_CLIENT_PASSWORD   | hard2guess        |
